<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>children (tekna) .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c1">" من مصر استدعيت <span class="c2">(متكلين)</span> ابناؤه <span class="c2">(تكنا)</span> . "</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
